  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d86\u0dba\u0dad\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "New appointments to several government agencies",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Cabinet Spokesman, Minister of Transport, Highways and Mass Media Dr. Bandula Gunawardena said today (26) that new heads have been appointed for several government institutions.",
        "Accordingly, DRS Hapuarachchi has been appointed as the Commissioner General of Inland Revenue, PBSC Nonis as the Director General of Customs, WA Satkumara as the Deputy Secretary of the Treasury and Jude Nilukshan as the Director General of the Information Technology Management Department. The minister mentioned.",
        "The Minister also said that the Cabinet Papers for these appointments were presented by President Ranil Wickremesinghe as the Minister of Finance.",
        "The minister said this while addressing the press conference to inform the Cabinet decisions held today (26) at the Government Information Department."
      ],
